---
title: Sheet Pan Sausage & Arugula Sandos with Melty Mozz, Pink Sauce & Potato Wedges
description: Sausage and peppers are a classic duo so we put on our matchmaking hats and thought, “Why not pair Italian pork sausage with something else peppery?” Enter: arugula! This bright, crisp green has a peppery bite that’s a natural match for rich, savory sausage. The two join up in these hoagie-style sandwiches with creamy tomato sauce and melty mozzarella cheese. With roasted potato wedges on the side, this entire meal is #relationshipgoals!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sheet-pan-sausage-arugula-sandos-7d7a47a9.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sheet-pan-sausage-arugula-sandos-61b0cf30f966ae533649df72-defd6b77.pdf
